### Building the Package

To build the package:

```bash
python -m pip install build
python -m build
```

Or using uv:

```bash
uv build
```

### Publishing to PyPI

To publish the package to PyPI:

```bash
python -m pip install twine
python -m twine upload dist/*
```

Or using uv:

```bash
uv publish
```

